### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5005/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "confirmPassword": "Password123!"
}

### Login with user
POST http://localhost:5005/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Get available roles (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:5005/api/user-roles/available-roles
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..1ra7Oqla3pg7mhm98mVQeyLvvh9jQpd1EM--NkAXyAM

### Change user role (requires Administrator role)
PUT http://localhost:5005/api/user-roles/change-role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..1ra7Oqla3pg7mhm98mVQeyLvvh9jQpd1EM--NkAXyAM

{
  "userId": "726d5c82-170f-41a4-840a-2632360adb89",
  "roleName": "Administrator"
}
